oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Summer Songwriting Camp Showcase - 2018-06-16
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performances of original songs written by young songwriters during the Museum’s Summer Songwriting Camp from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on June 16, 2018.
